videos.description: Green Bay coach Linc Darner sits down with Mike Tirico and Dan Dakich to talk about his first NCAA Tournament appearance and the team's first since 1996 after a 78-69 win over Wright State in the Horizon League title game.
videos.headline: Green Bay head coach: 'We stuck with it all year'
